refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public voidSplFileObject::setMaxLineLen intmaxLength
Sets the maximum length of a line to be read.

&reftitle.parameters;




   maxLength



     The maximum length of a line.

&reftitle.errors;


 Throws DomainException when
 maxLength is less than zero.

  &reftitle.examples;



    SplFileObject::setMaxLineLen example


<?php
$file = new SplFileObject("lipsum.txt");
$file->setMaxLineLen(20);
foreach ($file as $line) {
    echo $line . "\n";
}
?>



